Media, Entertainment Businesses Seen Growing Steadily, FT Says

-- B y   A l a n   P u r k i s s
-- 
2011-06-14T04:54:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-14/media-entertainment-businesses-seen-growing-steadily-ft-says.html
Media and entertainment businesses
are likely to grow at a compound annual rate of 5.7 percent
globally in the next five years, to $1.9 trillion in 2015,
according to an annual study by PricewaterhouseCoopers LLP, the
Financial Times reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alan Purkiss in  London  on   apurkiss@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 